
ARM CORTEX A9 Derleme Notlari

1. gnueabihf -> hf hard float, a9 icin bu secilecek.

2. PATH e /usr/local/toolchain_arm/bin dizinini ekle

3. Library derlemelerindeki prefixlerin home da olmasi, "Ranlib" in "sudo make install" da path de tanimli olmamasi ve hata vermesi yuzunden

4. Tavsiye edilen ARM Cortex A9 optimizasyon flagleri;
	
	-O3 -pipe -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a9 -mfloat-abi=hard -mvectorize-with-neon-quad -mfpu=neon -fassociative-math

5. MAC de toolchainler case sensitive partition/image de olmak zorunda...







//ZLib Derlemesi ========================>

ARM Cortex 15-----
CFLAGS='-O3 -pipe -march=armv7ve -mcpu=cortex-a15 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' CHOST=arm-linux-gnueabihf ./configure --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c15/4.9

ARM Cortex 9-----
CFLAGS='-O3 -pipe -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a9 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' CHOST=arm-linux-gnueabihf ./configure --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c9/4.8

ARM Cortex 8-----
CFLAGS='-O3 -pipe -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a8 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' CHOST=arm-linux-gnueabihf ./configure --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c8/4.8

ARM Cortex 7-----
CFLAGS='-O3 -pipe -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a7 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon-vfpv4 -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' CHOST=arm-linux-gnueabihf ./configure --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c7/4.8

PI------
CFLAGS='-O2 -pipe -march=armv6zk -mtune=arm1176jzf-s -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=vfp -marm' CHOST=arm-linux-gnueabihf ./configure --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/pi/4.8

make
make install






//OpenSSL Derlemesi ========================>

ARM icin optimize openssl

https://git.linaro.org/people/ard.biesheuvel/openssl.git adresinde, burdan clone yap.

ARM Cortex 15 ODROID XU3-----
CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- CC='gcc -O3 -pipe -DOPENSSL_SMALL_FOOTPRINT -march=armv7ve -mcpu=cortex-a15 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' ./Configure dist --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c15/4.9

ARM Cortex 9 ODROID U3-----
CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- CC='gcc -O3 -pipe -DOPENSSL_SMALL_FOOTPRINT -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a9 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' ./Configure dist --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c9/4.8

ARM Cortex 8 BEAGLEBONE BLACK-----
CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- CC='gcc -O3 -pipe -DOPENSSL_SMALL_FOOTPRINT -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a8 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' ./Configure dist --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c8/4.8

ARM Cortex 7 PI V2-----
CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- CC='gcc -O3 -pipe -DOPENSSL_SMALL_FOOTPRINT -march=armv7-a -mtune=cortex-a7 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon-vfpv4 -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' ./Configure dist --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c7/4.8

ARM11 PI V1------
CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabihf- CC='gcc -O2 -pipe -DOPENSSL_SMALL_FOOTPRINT -march=armv6zk -mtune=arm1176jzf-s -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=vfp -marm' ./Configure dist --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/pi/4.8

make depend
make
make install






//JSON-C derlemesi  ========================>

Json Source unu indir,

https://github.com/json-c/json-c

kurulu degilse, "autoconf" ve "libtool" kutuphanelerini brew den indir.

configure.ac dosyasindaki, 

AC_FUNC_MALLOC
AC_FUNC_REALLOC satirlarini commentout et, onune "#" koyarak, yoksa linkte rpl_malloc hatalarini alirsin.

CC yi geri unset et

unset CC
./autogen.sh

ARM Cortex 15-----
CFLAGS='-O3 -pipe -march=armv7ve -mcpu=cortex-a15 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=neon -mvectorize-with-neon-quad' ./configure --host=arm-linux-gnueabihf --prefix=/Volumes/Toolchains/libs/c15/4.9

ARM Cortex 9-----
